   firt we should create the file how to we create the file:
   1- when we right click on the our project then we create the Directory the rename the directory
   then we should right click on the Directory and make a file then we should store the data
   inside of the file then we should right click on the
   file and cope path then we create class in java and past on the String of the class. then
   we should move the Ram how we should mover to the RAM? we should create this code:
   String path="C:\\Users\\malik\\IdeaProjects\\JavaReview\\files\\Cinfig.properties";
           System.out.println(path);
           // moves the file from permanent storage into the RAM.
           FileInputStream file=new FileInputStream(path);
           //That one class/Software that will assist us to read Write the data from the file.
           Properties properties=new Properties();
           properties.load(file);
                   System.out.println(properties.get("userName"));
                   System.out.println(properties.get("Password"));
                   System.out.println(properties.get("URL"));



